 Introduction
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Access to the &lt;a href="https://x.com/"&gt;X&lt;/a&gt; social media platform (formerly known as Twitter) has &lt;a href="https://www.bbc.com/news/articles/cx2e1y02w21o"&gt;reportedly been blocked&lt;/a&gt; on networks in Tanzania since May 2025. This document provides an Expert Opinion by the &lt;a href="https://ooni.org/"&gt;Open Observatory of Network Interference (OONI) Foundation&lt;/a&gt; on this block.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>